'''Trader's Alley''' was a large cash-only bazaar located in [[Blue Level (Errant Venture)|Blue Level]] of [[Booster Terrik]]'s [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial''-class Star Destroyer]] ''[[Errant Venture/Legends|Errant Venture]]''. One of the greatest free markets in the [[The galaxy/Legends|galaxy]], the Trader's Alley did boast quite a selection of wares, legal or otherwise. Broken war [[Droid/Legends|droids]], captured [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] weapons, illegal drugs and [[Spice/Legends|spices]] and unique pieces of art from across the galaxy could be found in the Trader's Alley, no matter how restricted elsewhere.

In [[11 ABY/Legends|11 ABY]], [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] paid the bazaar a visit while he stayed aboard the [[Starship/Legends|ship]] for parts of his journey into and out of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]].

